---
---
<div class="bg-neutral-50 py-10 lg:py-20 pb-14">
    <div class="inline-flex flex-col items-center w-full px-4 lg:px-0">
        <h1 class="text-center justify-center text-black text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-10 lg:leading-[72px]">
            Run Your <span class="text-primary-500">Business</span> <br>
            <span class="flex justify-center items-center flex-wrap">
                Smarter
                <img class="mt-3 mx-3.5 h-8.5 md:h-9 lg:h-auto" src="/images/icons/toggle.svg" alt="">
                with Sales Zote.
            </span>
        </h1>
        <div class="max-w-[996px] text-center text-black text-base font-medium leading-snug mt-6">
            SalesZote is a modern POS and inventory management solution designed to streamline your operations, reduce stockouts, and give you actionable insights.
            Whether you're running a retail shop, wholesale outlet or growing chain, it's efficient, reliable and built for the way you do business.
        </div>

        <a href="https://app.saleszote.com/register" class="px-4 py-3 rounded-lg inline-flex bg-primary-500 border-1 border-primary-500 text-white text-base font-medium font-main leading-snug mt-9">
            Get Started For Free
        </a>

        <img class="hidden lg:block mt-10 max-w-[900px] xl:max-w-[1206px]" src="/images/hero-image.png" alt="SalesZote dashboard">
        <img class="lg:hidden mt-10 max-w-[360px] sm:max-w-[600px] md:max-w-[750px] mb-10" src="/images/hero-image-sm.png" alt="SalesZote mobile dashboard">

        <h2 class="text-center justify-start text-black text-xl sm:text-4xl font-bold leading-10">Used and Loved by Real Businesses</h2>
        <div class="max-w-[918px] text-center justify-start text-black text-base font-medium leading-snug">
            From local shops to growing chains, these businesses rely on SalesZote every day to power their operations
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-8xl mt-5">
        <!-- Desktop: Show all logos -->
        <div class="hidden lg:flex items-center justify-center w-full">
            <img class="h-12 w-auto mx-5" src="/images/clients/grabadrink.png" alt="Grab a Drink">
            <img class="h-12 w-auto mx-5" src="/images/clients/planty_kenya.png" alt="Planty Kenya">
            <img class="h-12 w-auto mx-5" src="/images/clients/organic.png" alt="Organic">
            <img class="h-12 w-auto mx-5" src="/images/clients/malizote.png" alt="Malizote">
            <img class="h-12 w-auto mx-5" src="/images/clients/street.png" alt="Street">
            <img class="h-12 w-auto mx-5" src="/images/clients/megamart.png" alt="Megamart">
        </div>

        <!-- Mobile: Auto-sliding carousel -->
        <div class="lg:hidden relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="flex animate-scroll">
                <!-- First set of logos -->
                <img class="h-10 w-auto mx-5 flex-shrink-0" src="/images/clients/grabadrink.png" alt="Grab a Drink">
                <img class="h-10 w-auto mx-5 flex-shrink-0" src="/images/clients/planty_kenya.png" alt="Planty Kenya">
                <img class="h-10 w-auto mx-5 flex-shrink-0" src="/images/clients/organic.png" alt="Organic">
                <img class="h-10 w-auto mx-5 flex-shrink-0" src="/images/clients/malizote.png" alt="Malizote">
                <img class="h-10 w-auto mx-5 flex-shrink-0" src="/images/clients/street.png" alt="Street">
                <img class="h-10 w-auto mx-5 flex-shrink-0" src="/images/clients/megamart.png" alt="Megamart">
                <!-- Duplicate set for seamless loop -->
                <img class="h-10 w-auto mx-5 flex-shrink-0" src="/images/clients/grabadrink.png" alt="Grab a Drink">
                <img class="h-10 w-auto mx-5 flex-shrink-0" src="/images/clients/planty_kenya.png" alt="Planty Kenya">
                <img class="h-10 w-auto mx-5 flex-shrink-0" src="/images/clients/organic.png" alt="Organic">
                <img class="h-10 w-auto mx-5 flex-shrink-0" src="/images/clients/malizote.png" alt="Malizote">
                <img class="h-10 w-auto mx-5 flex-shrink-0" src="/images/clients/street.png" alt="Street">
                <img class="h-10 w-auto mx-5 flex-shrink-0" src="/images/clients/megamart.png" alt="Megamart">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
